These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, video-games, gardening, singing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, cycling, parkour, climbing
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is cycling##2
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
3. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
4. the person who's sport is cycling is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | singing  | photography | gardening | video-games  |
| Sport   | skateboarding | parkour   | climbing  | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, cranberry, asparagus, cauliflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, writer, fisherman, dressmaker
1. the dressmaker is not to the left of the dressmaker##8
2. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating mango is the writer##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating mango and the person eating cranberry##2
5. the person eating cranberry is somewhere between the person eating asparagus and the social-worker##7
6. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the person eating cranberry##5
7. the social-worker is not to the left of the social-worker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | asparagus | cranberry          | cauliflower | mango     |
| Job    | fisherman      | dressmaker | social-worker | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, videographer, analyst, dancer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, thriller, sports, spy
1. the person watching zombie movies is not to the left of the analyst##8
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the teacher##1
4. the videographer is in an even position##4
5. the dancer is on the far left or far right##3
6. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
7. the dancer is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | teacher | videographer | analyst     | dancer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | spy   | zombie | sports    |

