.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, salsa, classical, ambient
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, skiing, rowing, rugby
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
4. the fan of ambient is not to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##8
5. the fan of house is the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the fan of house is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the fan of classical is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | classical   | salsa         | ambient   | house    |
| Sport         | skiing | rugby | rowing | basketball |

