.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, disaster, crime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, water-polo, volleyball
1. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##7
2. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
3. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching fantasy movies##7
4. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person watching mystery movies and the person who's sport is skiing##7
6. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##8
8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | disaster | crime | fantasy    |
| Sport         | badminton | volleyball   | water-polo   | skiing |

