2. the fan of trance is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the fan of house##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the person eating pear is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
7. the person eating pear is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pear | peach | orange  | pumpkin |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | reggae         | house | r&b |

