.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, lemonade, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, basketball, skiing, golf
1. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
2. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person who's sport is skiing##7
3. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5
4. the person who's sport is golf is not to the left of the person who's sport is handball##8
5. the person who's sport is golf is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
7. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | lemonade | hot-chocolate | juice   |
| Sport      | handball | skiing | golf  | basketball |

