3. the architect is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere between the person who's sport is rowing and the architect##7
5. the manager is not to the right of the librarian##8
6. the librarian is somewhere between the person who's sport is rowing and the manager##7

.:: Answer ::.
