.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, funk, salsa, ambient
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, subway, roller, train
1. the fan of r&b is between the fan of ambient and the person driving the ship##2
2. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
4. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
5. the person driving the subway is the person driving the subway##1
6. the fan of salsa is not the person driving the roller##6
7. the fan of ambient is not to the right of the fan of salsa##8
8. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | r&b | salsa | funk |
| Transport     | train | subway       | ship  | roller    |

