.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, kale, peach, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, skydiving, card-games, baking
1. the person eating peach is not to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##8
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person eating kale##8
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating peach is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
6. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | kale        | cherry | peach      | radish    |
| Hobby   | gardening | card-games   | skydiving | baking |

