.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, milk, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, golf, parkour, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the person drinking tea##7
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | sprite | tea         | milk    | iced-tea       |
| Sport      | golf | volleyball | water-polo | parkour |

