4. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking water and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is reading##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | cola     | iced-tea | water        | lemonade       |
| Hobby      | skydiving | dancing  | photography | reading |

