.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, plum, apple, peas
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, satire, documentary, action
 1. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
 2. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person eating apple##8
 3. the person eating corn is the person watching documentary movies##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the person watching satire movies##8
 5. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
 7. the person watching satire movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating corn is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8
 9. the person watching satire movies is not to the left of the person eating corn##8
10. the person eating plum is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | plum    | apple | corn | peas |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | action  | documentary     | satire    |

