.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, orange, carrot, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, chess, rock-climbing, board-games
1. the person eating carrot is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##8
3. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating orange##1
6. the person eating orange is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person eating zucchini##2
7. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | zucchini        | orange | apple | carrot |
| Hobby   | board-games | rock-climbing | chess   | skydiving    |

