.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, bird, hedgehog
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, bus, motorbike, boat
1. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person driving the motorbike##6
2. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
3. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the hedgehog##7
4. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
5. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
6. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the person driving the bus##8
7. the owner of the ferret is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | chinchilla  | hedgehog | ferret  | bird  |
| Transport   | skateboard | bus   | boat | motorbike |

