.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, lizard, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, roller, bus
1. the person driving the skateboard is not the owner of the mouse##6
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
4. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the taxi##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the taxi##7
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the bus and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | pony    | guinea-pig | mouse | lizard |
| Transport   | skateboard | bus      | roller     | taxi     |

 